result.name: 陳六記飯店

reviews.text: Reasonable prices, good service from friendly people.

The food here is more like rustic, home-cooked, traditional Chinese style. The pricing is reasonable and portion is fair. It's located a little out of the way, and might take a while or asking to find it. Note: menu is only in Chinese.
Tasted great.. Local food at its best.好好味，靚。
The roast pork is soggy. Not crispy at all

The reason we went there to eat is because they one of the few restaurants in Sheng Shui to have outdoor seatings. But to our surprise, the roasted pork belly (Charbroiled 5 story pork belly) was devilishly delicious. The meat literally melts in your mouth. However, this dish more suitable for 4 people instead of two because of its fat. The rest of the other dishes are all within HK small restaurant standard.

reviews.text: 係爭咗啲裝修咋😋
一個有歷史的飯店😊
上水其中一間老店，它的燒肉是其中一樣招牌菜，肥瘦雙間是幾好食，午餐或晚餐大約50幾60元但是不包飲品，但包一例湯，價錢一般。是可以一嘗
燒腩幾好食，但燒味雙拼飯分量太少
